'''Debra J. Fisher''' is an [[United States|American]] [[television writer]] and [[Television producer|producer]]. She has written episodes for television series such as ''[[Alias (TV series)|Alias]]'', ''[[The O.C.]]'', ''[[Charmed]]'', ''[[Criminal Minds]]'', ''[[The Forgotten (TV series)|The Forgotten]]'', ''[[Law & Order: Los Angeles]]'', ''[[Twisted (TV series)|Twisted]]'' and ''[[Witches of East End]]''. She has also been a co-producer of ''Charmed'' and ''Criminal Minds'', as well as a [[Head Writer|story editor]] on ''Alias'' and executive story editor on ''The O.C.''.

